AJLK-05 EMBROIDERED POLY CHIFFON 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Poly Chiffon Trouser: Malai Dupatta: Poly Net Fabric composition: Blended Color: Black

This elegant black ensemble, adorned with intricate embroidery on the front, is like a night sky. Its timeless color exudes sophistication and charm, making your child feel like a little royalty. The matching palazzo trousers add a touch of modern flair, while the flowing dupatta completes the look, perfect for any formal occasion. Let your kid be the epitome of style in this stunning outfit.
